{"tid":1883222,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"依個時勢 屋企有人對你吐口水 應該點做","createTime":"2020-02-16T20:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T18:33:50.000Z","uid":6097,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ba57616c6ce101c07871e5fcc95a1eec15156065","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T20:05:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1849842\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1849842</a><br />\n<br />\n因為佢日日無工開都堅持要出去<br />\n所以最後我都係lock佢門 <br />\n就咁lock 6pm-11pm<br />\n<br />\n之後講過好多次沖完涼要閂實門<br />\n因為如果佢本身有病 水蒸氣就全部有病毒<br />\n而且我哋廁所聞到類似渠味 係咪更加要閂門？<br />\n<br />\n今日發佢老皮叫佢閂門 <br />\n佢對我吐口水「一齊死啦 仆街」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我依家應該點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f682b2e05e60b62550549a8e8ce258f7ec8225c3","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T20:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6c6d384e8daed6861c341233b4e418bf71d822","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T20:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e30720e66750a8c6dd308d8df7e2ddda73d7aef","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T20:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=