000Z","msg":"我開頭條link已經係講過 <br />\n<br />\n因為知佢無工返 就日日重用口罩其實已經想lock<br />\n透過tg講過佢日日出又唔買又唔排口罩<br />\n<br />\n我就快頂唔住要lock門 前提係已經講過<br />\n之後姑姐係送咗盒口罩畀佢 得24+9塊<br />\n佢就日日出去吃喝玩樂 搵大陸朋友<br />\n去到樓下就除口罩 <br />\n<br />\n撘正我哋食飯時間返嚟 有兩次一入門口就咳<br />\n我最後警告過佢 佢點到要出去食飯 <br />\n我就lock6-11 講明係我喺屋活動時間 <br />\n其餘時間我喺房 門無lock<br />\n<br />\n因為我停課 我有做好自己日日唔出街 <br />\n除咗凌晨落去買之後一星期嘅食糧<br />\n<br />\n請問我有邊到做得唔夠？值得佢吐兩篤口水？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:17:08.000Z","msg":"講咁多做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:28:19.000Z","msg":"唔明 即係就算咁 我點都係錯哂嗰個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:42:44.000Z","msg":"唔夠強就收皮<br />\n弱肉強食有無聽過？<br />\n和平只係強者嘅選擇，弱嘅一方永遠無say<br />\n你想和平，佢想唔想？咁邊個強勢好明顯啦"},{"pid":"621a873a206c57d8157b0e584f09c7122309517d","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T22:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BGn4uj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BGn4uj.png&h=b123394e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrRfE2G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrRfE2G.png&h=caa7754d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nX0oOWX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnX0oOWX.png&h=14a84e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係乜都唔講/或者直情明知佢返工都lock/完全唔畀返"},{"pid":"8c45c3942a6ade5cca9bedd7ef8432ba44186813","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bb0bfc9fdb6605801f8a2b94ca01da8c99a3809","tid":1883222,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d4be1677a4b087aa050015c25886d1be1f6b78c","tid":1883222,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8055876d22318a3e749714b874929e19dd802e62","tid":1883222,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislik